msgid ""
"Reset your #{config.product_name} password\n"
"\n"
"<div>Hi #{user.firstname},</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>We received a request to reset the password for your "
"#{config.product_name} account <b>#{user.login}</b>.</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>If you want to reset your password, click on the link below (or copy "
"and paste the URL into your browser):</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div><a href=\"#{url}\">#{url}</a></div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>This link takes you to a page where you can change your password.</"
"div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>If you don't want to reset your password, please ignore this message. "
"Your password will not be reset.</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Your #{config.product_name} Team</div>\n"
msgstr ""
"Obnovte svoje heslo pre #{config.product_name}\n"
"\n"
"<div>Dobrý deň, #{user.firstname},</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Obdržali sme žiadosť o obnovenie hesla k vášmu účtu "
"#{config.product_name} <b>#{user.login}</b>.</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Ak chcete obnoviť svoje heslo, kliknite na nasledujúci odkaz (alebo "
"skopírujte a vložte URL adresu do svojho prehliadača):</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div><a href=\"#{url}\">#{url}</a></div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Tento odkaz vás presmeruje na stránku, kde si môžete zmeniť heslo.</"
"div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Ak si nechcete obnoviť heslo, ignorujte túto správu. Vaše heslo nebude "
"zmenené.</div>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<div>Váš tím #{config.product_name}</div>\n"

